    <item>
      <title>乌拉圭左翼党承诺若赢得大选将实现财政盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uruguay-s-left-party-pledges-fiscal-surplus-if-it-wins-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据乌拉圭反对党广泛阵线的总统候选人亚曼杜·奥尔西 (Yamandu Orsi) 挑选的财政部长候选人、经济学家加布里埃尔·奥多内 (Gabriel Oddone) 透露，如果他赢得 10 月份的选举，乌拉圭领先的总统候选人亚曼杜·奥尔西 (Yamandu Orsi) 将力争在其任期结束前实现初步财政盈余，并可能缩小该国的通胀目标区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uruguay-s-left-party-pledges-fiscal-surplus-if-it-wins-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:51:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023 年雪佛龙向非洲石油国家支付的费用超过美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/chevron-cvx-paid-more-in-tax-to-african-petrostates-than-us-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司2023年向尼日利亚、安哥拉和赤道几内亚缴纳了62.5亿美元的税款和石油产量分成，是该公司向美国政府缴纳金额的三倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/chevron-cvx-paid-more-in-tax-to-african-petrostates-than-us-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与真主党战争蔓延之际，伊朗新领导人登上联合国舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安周二在纽约首次出席联合国大会，提出两项紧迫但相互矛盾的任务：缓解伊朗的经济孤立，同时应对以色列与真主党不断升级的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
